        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '*The The Shrine of Ru\'Avitau is full of magic aggro, so even mages should bring along Silent Oil and Prism Powder.\n   - Note that Ninjutsu and Spectral Jig are also options for applying Sneak (Status) and Invisible (Status) without potentially aggroing nearby enemies.\n1. You may need someone to operate the Yellow door. The closest Monolith to your location is around I/J-9/10.\n2. Go to (I-6) in Ru\'Aun Gardens and enter the Shrine. You\'ll be on Map 1. Sneak and head south. Go past (J-7) through the first yellow door. Go west from here, to the room with 2 Monoliths in (H-7). You\'ll need Invisible, then go south around the square hallway filled with Aura Statue to another room with 2 Dark Elementals around (H-10).\n3. Go north, down a flight of stairs to the Celestial Nexus at (H-9).\n4. Gather together and get ready for the last BC of the expansion. You\'ll be fighting Eald\'narche, who has two forms.',
